The '''games room''' in a [[player-owned house]] is a place to play games and have fun. This room can be created at 30 [[Construction]], costing {{Coins|25000}}. Players who win at one of these games may obtain a [[prize key]], which can be used to receive a reward from the prize chest.

There are 5 [[hotspot]]s available to build games:
*[[Elemental balance space]]
*[[Game space]]
*[[Prize chest space]]
*[[Ranging game space]]
*[[Stone space]]

==Elemental balance==
Players are to use the elemental spells (air, earth, fire and water) to balance the colour of the orb white. Staves can not be used to substitute runes to build any elemental balance.
